 * Homepage v4 — light-first, editorial, no decorative effects.
 * Two visual concepts share this structure:
 *   A (default) Swiss Editorial — all-light, black CTAs, Swiss-red labels
 *   B Premium Technology — selected dark sections, deep ink-blue accent
 * Positioning: complete AI implementation & growth platform. The phone
 * agent appears as implementation proof, not as the identity.
 */
